      "fontSize": 18,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "Same asset (BTC) on Gate at -14.68% APR funding   →   LONG here, you RECEIVE 14.68%\nSame asset (BTC) on Hyperliquid at +10.96% APR funding   →   SHORT here, you RECEIVE 10.96%\nNet: +25.64% APR, delta-neutral on price (cash-and-carry)",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 18,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Same asset (BTC) on Gate at -14.68% APR funding   →   LONG here, you RECEIVE 14.68%\nSame asset (BTC) on Hyperliquid at +10.96% APR funding   →   SHORT here, you RECEIVE 10.96%\nNet: +25.64% APR, delta-neutral on price (cash-and-carry)",
