      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "❌  Moralis / CoinGecko / Birdeye  →  no perp funding rates\n❌  Coinglass  →  no public WebSocket\n❌  CEX direct  →  7 different APIs to manage\n\n✅  Mobula  →  1 WSS subscription = 7 venues, 1 unified message\n✅  Refresh every 10s\n✅  Includes CeFi (Binance, Bybit…) AND DeFi (Hyperliquid, Lighter)",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 16,
